    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and it's in really solid shape! It's been super well-loved and taken care of, so it runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something reliable that looks great on the road without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
